        public static void register(DBlock block,
                            java.util.function.Supplier<DTileEntity> tileEntity,
                            java.lang.String id)
        Register a custom DBlock and associate it with a given DTileEntity. This can be called with the same DTileEntity and id more than once, if you want to assign it to mulitple blocks.
        Parameters:
        block - The DBlock to register and associate with.
        tileEntity - A supplier that provides a new instance of the DTileEntity when required
        id - A unique id that will be used to identify the DTileEntity.
